Center: Russian Nuclear Structure and Reaction Data Centre, Kurchatov Institute, Moscow, Russia
title: Production of strong, high-energy neutron fluxes in a cyclotron by irradiating thick lithium and beryllium targets with 22-MeV deuterons.

x4freetext: Production of strong, high-energy neutron fluxes in a
cyclotron by irradiating thick lithium and beryllium

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Atomic Energy, Vol.30, p.493 (1971)

x4freetext: Thick lithium and beryllium targets ware used.
"all-wave" detector with a BF3 counter of the
SNM-5 type for measuring the absolute yields of
neutrons of all energies in the direction 0.degr.
relative to the irradiating deuteron beam.
